                </a>
                <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading"><a href="https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/dotnet/2017/09/28\net-framework-4-7-1-runtime-and-compiler-features/">.NET Framework 4.7.1 Runtime and Compiler Features</a></h4>
                <p>This post describes the new Runtime, Compiler and Base Class Library (BCL) improvements in the .NET Framework 4.7.1.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="media">
                <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                <img class="media-object" src="holder.js/90x90?bg=68217A&text=Scott Hanselman">
                </a>
