                <h4 class="media-heading"><a href="https://www.hanselman.com/blog/TabsVsSpacesAPeacefulResolutionWithEditorConfigInVisualStudioPlusNETExtensions.aspx">Tabs vs Spaces - A peaceful resolution with EditorConfig in Visual Studio. Plus .NET Extensions!</a></h4>
